name: digiNERATES -> Phuket Francis
description: The foreign city is a visual feast. No photo be it high def or disposable will ever beat the experience of these places. He thinks of how fleeting the moment is, how there are infinite more places to visit, but then he breathes the air, listens carefully, appreciates, solidifying the memory. Maybe he’ll come back some day. | 2048x2732 mp4 | @damnsam
